Hash: SHA512

I hate ads. I love open source.



So I setup my own network wide ad blocker. Now I run Pi-Hole on my homelab and block ads across my phone, iPad, and laptop. No more trackers or malware either, now they're blocked at a DNS level. You should check out setting up your own. 

Here's a great resource: https://lnkd.in/eDBxYYji

This whole experience made me realize Pi-Hole is the pinnacle of FOSS. Simple software that is easy to setup and configure. It comes with a good ad blocker list out of the box and is super easy to use through their admin dashboard. The world needs more projects like this, not more AI study tools. 

Build real projects that you care about.

Check out the signed message:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/a3l6/linkedin-posts/refs/heads/main/pihole.txt.asc

